   IS_COMPLETE_LATTICE f D = rest_WeakOrder D f /\
                    (!M. (~(M = EMPTY) /\ (M SUBSET D)) ==> (IS_SOME (BIGINF f D M) /\ IS_SOME (BIGSUP f D M)))`


